descript.abstract: County UDO Zoning for areas within the County's Zoning Jurisdiction, (excluding Municipal Areas and ETJ Areas). Adopted April 24, 2008 Effective July 1, 2008Published on 03.11.2022
descript.purpose: Maintain Zoning layers and Overlays for analysis for planning purposes.
descript.supplinf: In addition to County Zoning , certain areas my be subject to overlays which may add different restrictions to the underlying Zoning types. Also Zoning cases are heard monthly and pending approval by the Board of Commission will be updated upon that approval. See-UDOOverlays.
